dialogue: Oh no. I hear traffic. Where are you?
Gaaa! It's a car call. He's using me to entertain himself while he's sitting in traffic.
I'll lose an hour of my life if I don't get him off the phone.
Do me a favor and look in your briefcase to see if my latest report is there.
And turn down your radio so I can hear you... and check your calendar on your PDA.
